      <abstract displayLabel="Abstract">This document provides a new Incident Handling framework dedicated to
                Operational Technology. This framework expands the traditional technical steps by
                giving an Incident Response procedure based on the event escalation and provides
                techniques for OT Digital Forensics. It includes an overview with general terms
                explanation and a list of unique properties of OT DFIR, the preparation that should
                be done to establish an OT Incident Response Team, and finally, the suggested OT
                Incident Handling framework in detail.</abstract>
